Class OnDemandIndexStats

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.hazelcast.monitor.impl.OnDemandIndexStats

  • public class OnDemandIndexStats
extends Object
    Holds the intermediate results while combining the partitioned index stats to produce the final per-index stats.
